   <category name='moves'>

      <section name='noexit'>

         <para number='1' comment='Stair ways and Cliff top'>
         You stumble and just barely manage to catch yourself just in time to keep from breaking your neck as you discover that you cannot go in that direction.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Underworld'>
         Only the dead may pass in that direction to the underworld.  Of course, if you like, that may be arranged....
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='Indoors Homes/offices'>
         You nearly knock a picture off the wall as you walk right into it.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='Pantheon interior'>
         You stumble and run into a mass of solid marble as you discover that you cannot go that way.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='Pub Bacchus'>
         A tangle of grape vines prevents travel in that direction.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Faunus Pad'>
         As you attempt to walk into the woods, you run into the wall.  It was just a hologram after all.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Hospital'>
         You stumble over an occupied gurney as you, unsuccessfully, try to exit in that direction.
         </para>

         <para number='8' comment='Mars weapons'>
         Sharp implements of war block travel along that path.
         </para>

         <para number='9' comment='Uranus and Saturn'>
         Stepping through the darkness you walk right into a wall bumping your head and stubbing your toe (or equivalent) on something very large and heavy.
         </para>

         <para number='10' comment='Venus and Vestals'>
         Your path is blocked by masses of gauzy drapes that entangle those who attempt to pass through.
         </para>

         <para number='11' comment='Piazza'>
         A sudden flurry of pigeons prevents you from traveling in that direction.
         </para>

         <para number='12' comment='garden path no woods'>
         A soft chime gently reminds you to stay on the cleared pathways.
         </para>

         <para number='13' comment='Hot tub and fountain'>
         You splash about in the water nearly drowning yourself.  After all that, you realize that there is no exit that way.
         </para>

         <para number='14' comment='Wooded path'>
         A low fence prevents you from leaving the path and getting lost in the woods.
         </para>

         <para number='15' comment='Dryad tree'>
         You hear a whisper behind you and a Dryad Goddess quietly advises you that you can't move in that direction.
         </para>

         <para number='16' comment='Library'>
         As you try to move in that direction, ou accidentally knock over a pile of books resulting in a loud crash.  The librarian looks up and shushes you and asks you to please be quiet.
         </para>

         <para number='17' comment='Terrace'>
         A tall privacy fence prevents tourists from seeing in and also prevents travel in that direction.
         </para>

      </section>

