         </para>

      </section>

      <section name='slot'>

         <para number='1' comment='Put coin in slot 2215 - no coin'>
         You do not have a coin to put into the slot.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Got coin so in it goes - player'>
         You don't have a 13-groat coin but fumbling in your pocket you find the triangular 7-groat piece you took from the fountain. Maybe that will do. You put it into the slot, but it doesn't fit very well. Giving it a shove, you insert it as far as it will go, until it is stuck fast. A red warning light begins to flash, and an alarm buzzes loudly. Everybody in the exchange looks at you to see what you have done.
         </para>

         <para number='3'>
         A repair technician appears and glares at you. "Another fool trying to use inappropriate currency in the slot machine," he mutters to himself, as he uses some kind of tool to remove the coin you mistakenly tried to insert. He resets the machine, which shuts off the alarm, then walks off, still grumbling, and taking your coin with him.
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='roomex'>
         You hear the sudden buzz of an alarm, and see a red warning light flashing on and off. Looking around for the cause, you notice that %s is looking embarrassed.
         </para>

         <para number='5'>
         A repair technician appears and you see him glaring at %s. He mutters to himself, "Another fool trying to use inappropriate currency in the slot machine," as he uses some kind of tool to remove the coin mistakenly inserted. He resets the machine, which shuts off the alarm, then walks off, still grumbling.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='Put coin in slot 2215 - no coin'>
         You do not have a token to put into the slot.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='Got token - player'>
         You insert your 13-groat token into the slot and it drops into the mechanism with a clunk. The machine's lights come on as it whirls to life and the screen starts displaying information.
         </para>

         <para number='8'>
         Details on the building and population of the Pantheon flash across the screen. Scanning it, you learn the amazing fact that this planet was built with only the Roman Gods and Goddesses in mind, and that mankind was merely an afterthought because they missed having worshippers.
         </para>

         <para number='9'>
         After a few shameless plugs for sponsors of tourism locations, the machine turns itself off.
         </para>

         <para number='10' comment='Roomex'>
         You hear the whirr of machinery, and looking around you see that the slot machine has sprung into life, apparently because of something %s has done. Lights flash and information scrolls across the screen, but it's too far away for you to read any of it.
         </para>

         <para number='11'>
         After a few moments, the machine turns itself off again.
         </para>

      </section>

